T1  - MULTIPLE DRUG USE IN SCHIZOPHRENIA - THE ROLE OF EARLY ENVIRONMENTAL RISK ACCUMULATION AND GENETIC PREDISPOSITION...Schizophrenia International Research Society (SIRS) 2020 Congress.
AU  - Steixner-Kumar, Agnes
