N1  - Accession Number: 106103315. Language: English. Entry Date: 20081219. Revision Date: 20231015. Publication Type: Journal Article. Journal Subset: Biomedical; Europe; Peer Reviewed; Public Health; UK & Ireland. NLM UID: 9106628. 
KW  - Abnormalities -- Etiology
KW  - Abnormalities
KW  - Environmental Pollutants -- Adverse Effects
