T1  - ENVIRONMENTAL RISK FACTORS IN BIPOLAR DISORDER AND PSYCHOTIC DEPRESSION: AÂ SYSTEMATIC REVIEW AND META-ANALYSIS OF PROSPECTIVE STUDIES...Schizophrenia International Research Society (SIRS) 2020 Congress
AU  - Rodriguez, Victoria
AU  - Alameda, Luis
AU  - Marino, Paolo
AU  - Trotta, Giulia
AU  - Spinazzola, Edoardo
AU  - Matheson, Sandra
AU  - Laurens, Kristin
